This paper deals with image reconstruction using machine learning techniques, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of regression functions and termination criteria, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The paper also deals with image acquisition and measurement, which is a topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Finally, the paper presents results on synthetic and experimental data, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
